Example 1: Validating Password
13Example of RequestDispatcher
interface
 In this example, we are validating the password entered by 
the user. 
 If password is valid, it will forward the request to the 
WelcomeServlet, 
 otherwise, will show an error message: “sorry username or 
password error!”. 
 In this program, we are checking for hardcoded information.
 In this example, we have created following files:
 index.html file: for getting input from the user.
 Login.java file: a servlet class for processing the response. If 
password is valid, it will forward the request to the welcome servlet.
 WelcomeServlet.java file: a servlet class for displaying the 
welcome message.
